    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/7e36fd5a0f6bd94712be55b03a67b693.avif?t=1766555239\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/68b60d0aa43e485fd491439b8605f34c.poster.avif?t=1766555239\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/68b60d0aa43e485fd491439b8605f34c.webm?t=1766555239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/68b60d0aa43e485fd491439b8605f34c.mp4?t=1766555239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>VIVA NOBOTS</strong> is a treasure-hunting stealth action game where humans (players) disguise themselves as excavation robots (NPCs) to sneak into ancient ruins.  <br>As a NOBOT — a treasure hunter in disguise — your goal is to get rich and rise to the top of the wanted rankings!<br><br>The key to being a successful NOBOT is <strong>“Can you steal the treasure without blowing your cover?”</strong>  <br>You can enter and leave the ruins at any time—<br>but beware: <strong>you never know how many rival players might be lurking inside!</strong><br>Dig for treasure while blending in with the bots, and if you spot another player, expose them and steal their loot!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/dc4894fc61780e85934ffbb4bf7982c4.webp?t=1766555239\" width=616 height=55 /></span>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/1cefbe088afb4890b21a5adfda00165f.poster.avif?t=1766555239\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/1cefbe088afb4890b21a5adfda00165f.webm?t=1766555239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/1cefbe088afb4890b21a5adfda00165f.mp4?t=1766555239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br><strong>Blend in with excavation robots and snatch treasures from ancient ruins!</strong>  <br>When three symbols align, treasure appears — time your dig carefully while keeping an eye on rivals!<br>The rarer the treasure, the stronger the buffs—and the higher the points!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/d326dc03be1b0565c3686888bad6f5c6.webp?t=1766555239\" width=616 height=55 /></span>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/1e93f1ebea8df1e0b44adb375506cd50.poster.avif?t=1766555239\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/1e93f1ebea8df1e0b44adb375506cd50.webm?t=1766555239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/1e93f1ebea8df1e0b44adb375506cd50.mp4?t=1766555239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br><strong>Spot a suspicious player? Use the Doubt Gun to reveal their true identity!</strong>  <br>Expose rivals to steal their treasure and earn bonus bounty rewards!  <br>But be careful — if you shoot a real NPC, you'll pay the price!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/d15e6b0c668b25e16bcd2ad541d96ae3.webp?t=1766555239\" width=616 height=55 /></span>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/6fd694c5cbc1c6311d9bffba73b98b9c.poster.avif?t=1766555239\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/6fd694c5cbc1c6311d9bffba73b98b9c.webm?t=1766555239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/6fd694c5cbc1c6311d9bffba73b98b9c.mp4?t=1766555239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Even if you grab the treasure, you're not safe until you escape!</strong>  <br>If your identity is revealed by rivals or security bots, they'll snatch your loot!  <br>However, if you successfully identify all three rivals, you can make a daring escape via the <strong>&quot;Victory Lap&quot;</strong> — no exit required!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/b58e909e1d1800b1430d1634228ba26e.poster.avif?t=1766555239\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/b58e909e1d1800b1430d1634228ba26e.webm?t=1766555239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/b58e909e1d1800b1430d1634228ba26e.mp4?t=1766555239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Open Beta Update</h2><strong>・New humanoid security bot: the “Android” is here!<br>・Hit the mega-jackpot with the “GODPOT” and strike it rich!<br>・Collect map pieces and head for the golden ruins, “Gol Dorado”!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/414676f19518266eea1a38e03d1d2b92.avif?t=1766555239\" width=616 height=350 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Future Update Plans</h2>・Co-op / VS Mode<br>・Change avatar type<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104370/extras/94bce42a0719d71aa8737b3cfebae863.avif?t=1766555239\" width=616 height=80 /></span>  ",
